      options: [{ id: `A`, text: `It contrasts Richard's wary first impressions of Adam with his ultimate affection for him.` }, { id: `B`, text: `It showcases how Adam's flexibility and consideration strengthen his relationship with his great-uncle Richard.` }, { id: `C`, text: `It gives the reasons the two decide to sleep on the ship rather than on land.` }, { id: `D`, text: `It explains why the two are excited for their upcoming journey.` }],
